PaCaLib: my 2D rendering library interface for Glesly
-----------------------------------------------------

This is an object-oriented interface to draw graphics primitives including lines, circles, text, etc...

It is based on the following libraries:
- makesys   https://github.com/kgy64/makesys.git        My build system
- baselib   https://github.com/kgy64/baselib.git        My basic library

The following implementations are available:
- Linux:
    pacalib-pango       https://github.com/kgy64/pacalib-pango.git      Pango/Cairo based implementation
    pacalib-android     https://github.com/kgy64/pacalib-android.git    Implementation for Android

